13	 * built?" but "once it is alive, do its SAFETY RAILS hold?" — capability gating at typecheck
14	 * (Act IV), live schema migration without data loss (Act III), the loop guard's self-write
15	 * exclusion (Act VI), payload validation as silent-drop (Act V), a code-handler hook that really
